12.short_description: Corporate Venture Studio

18.description:
Together with entrepreneurs, we promote traditional industries with startups.

There are two types of #CorporateVenturing, internal and external. Internally, the focus is on R&D and incremental innovation of the current business. The external (COCOCO) looks for new models with spin-offs outside the organization.

What does the CORPORATION contribute?
It transfers its experience and knowledge to the startup, gives it access to the market and makes all its resources, infrastructure, capital and production capacity available to it.

What does COCOCO provide?
COCOCO provides the methodology for creating companies: agility, innovation, mentality, recruitment of entrepreneurial talent, software, data, business and growth.

What will the new STARTUP contribute to the CORPORATION?
The startup transfers to the big company its motivation, passion and desire to break the mold, as well as its ability to manage risk and find new markets.

What does the startup bring to its partners?
New EBITDA multiplication engines for the main company and new digital assets in your industry.

Win-win objective where all parties benefit from this agreement. Giving incredible competitive advantages to the new startup that is born.
